<plot>Loosely based on the Greek myth of Pyramus and Thisbe, Hide &amp; Seek tells the tale of Elaine, a fantasy-obsessed woman, enclosed within the confines of her room as a result of a military-imposed captivity. Engrossed in her own version's of pulp romance, she strikes up an unusual friendship with George, a man in the unit next door. However, the air vent through which they communicate will also be their trap and possible exposure.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?238579</url></doc>
